輕人這邊 每個星期齊野餐"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:19.000Z","msg":"光明好快會嚟"},{"pid":"c728e9483abb5cadcb0f10dae50a5f20074e1dd9","tid":1379020,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T17:59:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ed4d5a97942dee693cc4e979b469dc0125c3e797","tid":1379020,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T18:03:41.000Z","msg":"捱打都要卸力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">防護裝備用完唔好亂掉，呢啲唔係武器，俾人搜到都唔怕。<br />\n俾人查身份證都驚就唔好學人講抗爭。</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">黑警問點解帶防具出街，你就答：<br />\n<strong><ins>而家警察落閘唔出勤，市民戴保護裝備出街好合理！<br />\n警察盡責嘅話，我洗攞咁多重野出街食飯？！<br />\n呢啲係冇攻擊性嘅防護措施，唔通海邊嘅救生圈、船上嘅救生衣都犯法？</ins></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>727有兩個情況嚴重，希望平安無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n728少好多full gear<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><em>所以話防具好重要，尤其係保命嘅電單車頭盔，工地安全帽唔夠保護性！</em></span><br />\n<ins><span style=\"color: orange;\">電單車頭盔要買snell安全標準嘅，聽講可以擋到時速500公里嘅氣槍</span></ins></strong></span>，詳細睇：<a href=\"https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fultimatemotorcycling.com%2F2013%2F04%2F08%2Fmotorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell%2F&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy%2BNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=d108d211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ultimatemotorcycling.com/2013/04/08/motorcycle-helmet-standards-explained-dot-ece-22-05-snell/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[多圖]純防護裝備：頭盔、盾</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372308\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372308</a>"},{"pid":"bf6fd0216aa38703b8761655203359